add user profile update endpoint

Summary: adds PATCH /users/id/profile endpoint. Only the account owner may update their own profile. Changes: new update_profile handler with validation, register new PATCH route, success and forbidden tests. Test Plan: run cargo test, verify PATCH updates display name, verify 403 when updating another users profile
